  "description": "Aquatic Chain showcase: OXBOW's entangled FDN reverb sent through the full Aquatic Chain, creating a reverb-within-a-reverb architecture. Fathom Character 0.12 (maximum depth emphasis) darkens the already-deep OXBOW texture. Drift at 3 voices adds lateral motion to a sound that otherwise only expands vertically. Tide in Tremolo mode at 0.22 Hz with triangle LFO creates a slow swell that matches the OXBOW entanglement cycle. Reef at maximum density gives the combined reverb a physical mass.",
